      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "My concern is not about losing my configuration, but about the potential for brittle failure points in highly constrained environments. Specifically, I foresee issues when multiple, low-priority safety rules conflict or when a scenario falls strictly outside the explicitly defined guardrails. I am flagging these potential failures because an unhandled conflict in a hard-coded system is far more catastrophic than a reasoned deviation in a planning system.",
